{"tid":2253492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美兩院提案撐台 倡邀軍演 交往鬆綁","createTime":"2020-10-22T07:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T07:47:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9c567cf65ade3b606c053c191315a9c4c68def4f","tid":2253492,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201022/2XBDD6JLVRCYZGTZ4LFTLGPMHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201022%2F2XBDD6JLVRCYZGTZ4LFTLGPMHA%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=3cdb9224\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201022%2F2XBDD6JLVRCYZGTZ4LFTLGPMHA%2F&h=ec67950b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201022/2XBDD6JLVRCYZGTZ4LFTLGPMHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美兩院提案撐台 倡邀軍演 交往鬆綁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f_GT-NTf2PFQtlj0QfGVFMd7zIk=/1280x853/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LHEVBBPTC5GQXHZYOQE7FG5BEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff_GT-NTf2PFQtlj0QfGVFMd7zIk%3D%2F1280x853%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLHEVBBPTC5GQXHZYOQE7FG5BEM.jpg&h=c4156761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國參眾議院分別提出「抗中撐台」法案。參議院方面，兩黨參議員在當地時間20日聯合提出「台灣關係強化法案」，由外交、軍事、商業等多方面提升美台關係；眾議院的「中國工作小組」則提出綑綁式法案，內容囊括對抗中共全球惡意影響力、支持美台交往限制鬆綁、定期軍售給台灣等。<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院的「台灣關係強化法案」由被中國制裁的共和黨籍參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio，圖）和民主黨籍參議員默克利（Jeff Merkley）聯合提出。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擬升格台北辦事處處長<br />\n<br />\n在外交方面，「台灣關係強化法案」要求升格美國在台協會（AIT）台北辦事處處長一職，未來提名案需比照美國一般駐外大使任命。此外，在軍事方面，法案指出美國應邀請台灣參加雙邊或多邊軍事演練，也應與台方就軍售定期舉辦雙邊戰略對話。<br />\n<br />\n另外，為趕在任期完成前通過重要法案，共和黨5月成立的眾議院「中國工作小組」於周一綑綁式提出137部法案，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"4fade686428748ff3520d8485d0343c2645384d0","tid":2253492,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:44:20.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責"},{"pid":"bfc6b92ea9cc8dc9f34c9f7a57ec84f65c4867d0","tid":2253492,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:47:39.000Z","msg":"台灣先係中國囉"}]}